  "bib_entries": {
    "124856240": {
      "title": "Circuit simulation and implement for fractional-order chaotic systems",
      "abstract": "To study the performances of Fractional-order chaotic system and its applications,a circuit simulation and design method of fractional-order chaotic systems were investigated based on the definition of fractional-order calculus operator.By designing the simulation model of the fractional-order integral operator and setting up simulation circuit of the fractional-order chaotic system,the simulations and analysis of fractional-order chaotic system were carried out.By simulating,the evolving process of system variable is observing,and the dynamics performances are analyzed conveniently by.The simulation results of the fractional-order diffusionless Lorenz system on EWB and its circuit complementation show that the circuit simulation and design approach are effective."
    }
  },
